{"tid":2517071,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"現時尿兜設計真係好落後","createTime":"2021-05-05T05:41:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T05:42:53.000Z","uid":35315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"df4fde9d559a94e8b577d10b6d3a2eecc7fd93ff","tid":2517071,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:41:11.000Z","msg":"男人老狗，去親廁所對住個尿兜屙尿永遠都要面對兩大難題<br />\n第一：尿兜彈尿／水，彈到褲／鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二：尿兜對落地下成日都有一灘混合尿液<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩大原因<br />\n第一：尿會係個尿兜彈返出黎<br />\n第二：廢J屙尿滴滴仔，無得救<br />\n所以我認為改善尿兜設計係最有效嘅方法<br />\n內容用小畫家劣畫，各位巴打見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n普遍尿兜，強調係<strong>普遍尿兜</strong>都係類似以下設計，下巴成兜狀<br />\n巴打們有一條稍有返少少力嘅JJ，即使有足球仔畀你瞄準，尿柱嘅衝擊力都足夠令大大小小嘅尿水珠／水花彈到周圍都係，褲／鞋成日中招<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BN8tQOu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBN8tQOu.png&h=200ccd5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而我一直有個迷思，點解尿兜要設計成兜狀，而唔係利用斜角反射減少回彈嘅可能性<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NVQcxXo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNVQcxXo.jpg&h=3dc48c4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n參考示範圖，利用反射角度可以將回彈到嘅尿花減至最低程度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sLHa36b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsLHa36b.png&h=720ead5b&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n申利: 我知個名同個Post 相映成趣，並不代表本人有前列線疾病<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e81549faae1a3eb93c7c7d751a7c7b5bdc99a2a","tid":2517071,"uid":263334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:42:53.000Z","msg":"用水樽屙算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}